{"tid":1988957,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"半年來首見！中國手機通過 NCC 認證、確定重返台灣市場","createTime":"2020-04-25T14:28:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-25T16:04:18.000Z","uid":75656,"like":1,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"3fb1279356f997cb1fbd4c999e1749cc73d9a3c5","tid":1988957,"uid":75656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T14:28:05.000Z","msg":"繼先前華為因於系統內顯示「中國台灣」，導致 NCC 開始要求品牌簽署切結書，進而使得從去年 11 月至 4 月這段期間，中國手機品牌一片靜悄悄，隨著 NCC 將規定法規化，如今中國手機終於可以避開敏感的政治議題，重返台灣市場。<br />\n<br />\n根據 NCC 認證網站，於 4 月 24 日中國品牌 realme 一共通過 4 款手機認證，是睽違半年再度有中國手機過關，即將登台開賣。本次獲得認證的型號分別為 RMX2030、RMX2040、RMX1931、RMX2020，分別代別 realme 5i、realme 6i、realme X2 Pro、realme C3。<br />\n<br />\n最受矚目的是旗艦款的 realme X2 Pro，搭載高通 S855+ 處理器，擁有 90Hz 刷新率、6.5 吋大螢幕以及 4,000 mAh 電量與 50W 快充，儘管不支援 5G 網路，但考慮到 realme 向來主打 CP 值的售價，與 4G 手機現在定價偏低，或許也能提供不急於使用 5G 網路的消費者，另一個划算的選擇。<br />\n<br />\n隨著 realme 順利過關，可預期後續 Oppo、vivo、小米、華為等，將陸續在近幾個月推出新機，小米 10、10 Pro 官方更已經證實，有在台灣上市的計畫。有鑒於 5G 手機大漲價，以性價比為亮點的中國品牌重返台灣市場，得以填補 2 萬元區間的產品空缺，讓消費者有更多選擇。<br />\n<br />\nNCC 三月增訂「電信終端設備審驗辦法」相關條文，修法通過後，原本切結書內容被法規化，未來品牌「形式上」不必觸碰敏感的政治字眼，解決了「簽不簽」切結書的壓力。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://3c.ltn.com.tw/news/40207\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2F3c.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2F40207&d=5PHCsmqc8bXRSfVPwy6hKj8W653rZVWOX%2F4zqp%2BjK3Y%3D&h=6983d83b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2F3c.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2F40207&h=8b8aff58\" target=\"_blank\">https://3c.ltn.com.tw/news/40207</a>"},{"pid":"3f4a74c3eebc8589d9a95d8a1b6377e7d914b7da","tid":1988957,"uid":25601,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T14:41:39.000Z","msg":"戰略性撒退<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n賣唔賣得出呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25c3e153e20a64a7cdd4c8abeedbc6337ff03e12","tid":1988957,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T15:13:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd17e3edfacb77163c67adcc4515267aa8eb1b8c","tid":1988957,"uid":193233,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T15:20:49.000Z","msg":"小粉紅又會點面對？"},{"pid":"615edc129dfd397b7c4523d24941b44c6ab7e0e7","tid":1988957,"uid":53481,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T15:29:34.000Z","msg":"中国製造嘅產品竟然唔強調中国台湾？<br />\n又想威，又想賺錢，慳啲啦屌你老母支那"},{"pid":"8f4448837fbe6a20fcfda248aec22cc9da7a2c4c","tid":1988957,"uid":179409,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fd17e3edfacb77163c67adcc4515267aa8eb1b8c","tid":1988957,"uid":193233,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T15:20:49.000Z","msg":"小粉紅又會點面對？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T15:49:33.000Z","msg":"傳返入支那<br />\n班支那仔肯定發癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"957093a1b542134d06278dd0a9929d444344aa43","tid":1988957,"uid":63029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T15:54:38.000Z","msg":"又話人哋台灣省<br />\n<br />\n直接運去啦洗撚批"},{"pid":"6890f6f243747043369bc07fb512a2c9e24967cc","tid":1988957,"uid":224066,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T15:59:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FaFqzf9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFaFqzf9.jpg&h=8bc2314e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ad57cc931bb839d406af8eeaf29e22e870086558","tid":1988957,"uid":266654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T16:04:18.000Z","msg":"咁都要有人買先得㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}